trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.MsmqTransportSecurityElement" /> class encapsulates the transport security settings for queued transports.
trans-unit.target: A classe <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.MsmqTransportSecurityElement" /> encapsula as configurações de segurança do transporte para transportes na fila.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.MsmqTransportSecurityElement" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.MsmqTransportSecurityElement" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqAuthenticationMode" /> that is associated with this instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define o <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqAuthenticationMode" /> associado a esta instância da classe <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqAuthenticationMode" /> that is associated with this instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" /> class.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqAuthenticationMode" /> que está associado esta instância do <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" /> classe.

trans-unit.source: Message Queuing (MSMQ) can authenticate messages that are sent to message queues that require authentication, or messages can explicitly request authentication.
trans-unit.target: Enfileiramento de mensagens (MSMQ) pode autenticar mensagens enviadas para filas de mensagens que exigem autenticação ou mensagens explicitamente podem solicitar a autenticação.
O modo de autenticação padrão é <xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqAuthenticationMode.WindowsDomain>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqEncryptionAlgorithm" /> that is associated with this instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define o <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqEncryptionAlgorithm" /> associado a esta instância da classe <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqEncryptionAlgorithm" /> that is associated with this instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" /> class.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqEncryptionAlgorithm" /> que está associado esta instância do <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" /> classe.

trans-unit.source: Message Queuing (MSMQ) can encrypt messages on the wire when transferring messages between message queue managers.
trans-unit.target: Serviço de enfileiramento de mensagens (MSMQ) pode criptografar mensagens na conexão durante a transferência de mensagens entre os gerenciadores de fila de mensagem.
O algoritmo de criptografia padrão é <xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqEncryptionAlgorithm.RC4Stream>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <see cref="T:System.Net.Security.ProtectionLevel" /> that is associated with this instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.MsmqTransportSecurityElement" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define o <see cref="T:System.Net.Security.ProtectionLevel" /> associado a esta instância da classe <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.MsmqTransportSecurityElement" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Net.Security.ProtectionLevel" /> that is associated with this instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" /> class.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Net.Security.ProtectionLevel" /> que está associado esta instância do <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" /> classe.
O nível de proteção padrão é <xref:System.Net.Security.ProtectionLevel.Sign>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqSecureHashAlgorithm" /> that is associated with this instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.MsmqTransportSecurityElement" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define o <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqSecureHashAlgorithm" /> associado a esta instância da classe <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.MsmqTransportSecurityElement" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqSecureHashAlgorithm" /> that is associated with this instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" /> class.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqSecureHashAlgorithm" /> que está associado esta instância do <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.MsmqTransportSecurity" /> classe.
O algoritmo de hash padrão é <xref:System.ServiceModel.MsmqSecureHashAlgorithm>.
